column5: I usually launch at Caesarea launch, but while fishing north end of the lake, towards the river to Lindsay, I saw a boat launch on my east, near Janetville?  Where is it exactly? Parking? Condition? Cost?  Thanks for input
was wondering the same thing .. I know for a fact theres a launch in View lake.. tho you basically have to beach your boat. but look on the plus side.. its free..
Yep, its in view lake. Just follow 57 east out of cesarea and you can't miss it. Its just a dirt ramp, and its kinda shallow with no dock. Its doable though.  Sinker
its where i launch most of the time as i find ceserea to be hectic with the nice weather
